msgid "We solve the static equilibrium of an isotropic linear elastic body:"
msgstr "我们求解各向同性线弹性体的静力平衡问题："

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:166
#: 32e1d3f8d30e44f3bc53848c335371e3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"    -\\nabla \\cdot \\boldsymbol{\\sigma}(\\mathbf{x}) = \\mathbf{f}(\\mathbf{x}) & \\text{in } \\Omega, \\\\\n"
"    \\mathbf{u}(\\mathbf{x}) = \\mathbf{0} & \\text{on } \\partial\\Omega,\n"
"\\end{cases}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{cases}\n"
"    -\\nabla \\cdot \\boldsymbol{\\sigma}(\\mathbf{x}) = \\mathbf{f}(\\mathbf{x}) & \\text{in } \\Omega, \\\\\n"
"    \\mathbf{u}(\\mathbf{x}) = \\mathbf{0} & \\text{on } \\partial\\Omega,\n"
"\\end{cases}"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:173
#: 30fb8c27ca0c473099208aee19d7edd5
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\mathbf{u} : \\Omega \\to \\mathbb{R}^3` is the displacement "
"and the Cauchy stress satisfies Hooke's law"
msgstr "其中 :math:`\\mathbf{u} : \\Omega \\to \\mathbb{R}^3` 为位移，柯西应力满足胡克定律"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:176
#: 9baebf2f36c841a69f7a728f93d02f44
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\boldsymbol{\\sigma} = \\lambda \\, \\mathrm{tr}(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}) \\, \\mathbf{I}\n"
"+ 2\\mu \\, \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon} = \\tfrac{1}{2}\\bigl(\\nabla \\mathbf{u} + (\\nabla \\mathbf{u})^\\top\\bigr)."
msgstr ""
"\\boldsymbol{\\sigma} = \\lambda \\, \\mathrm{tr}(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}) \\, \\mathbf{I}\n"
"+ 2\\mu \\, \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon} = \\tfrac{1}{2}\\bigl(\\nabla \\mathbf{u} + (\\nabla \\mathbf{u})^\\top\\bigr)."

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:183
#: 224494ca877c428b9d79d6acc52d91c3
msgid ""
"We set Young's modulus :math:`E = 1` and Poisson's ratio :math:`\\nu = 0.3`,"
" giving"
msgstr "我们取杨氏模量 :math:`E = 1`\\ 、泊松比 :math:`\\nu = 0.3`\\ ，由此得到"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:186
#: a558935204984d6291b86cc17adefd67
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\lambda = \\frac{E\\nu}{(1+\\nu)(1-2\\nu)},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mu = \\frac{E}{2(1+\\nu)}."
msgstr ""
"\\lambda = \\frac{E\\nu}{(1+\\nu)(1-2\\nu)},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\mu = \\frac{E}{2(1+\\nu)}."

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:192
#: 08c8e0f3a8e74b27bf008cfe746a8321
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"A constant body force :math:`\\mathbf{f} = (1,1,1)^\\top` is applied. To "
"introduce geometric complexity we use a hollow cube domain"
msgstr "施加常数体力 :math:`\\mathbf{f} = (1,1,1)^\\top`\\ 。为引入几何复杂度，我们采用空心立方体区域"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:195
#: c6fe2f5b6b96494e8d3e758abe0f0c4a
msgid "\\Omega = [0,1]^3 \\setminus (0.25,\\, 0.75)^3."
msgstr "\\Omega = [0,1]^3 \\setminus (0.25,\\, 0.75)^3."

