#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:238
#: 767a49bb82ac4be98dcb8d2ec98227fa
msgid ""
"The inverse-problem benchmark exercises the **differentiability** of "
"TensorMesh on a classical topology-optimization task: compliance "
"minimization of a 2D cantilever beam using the Solid Isotropic Material with"
" Penalization (SIMP) method. We compare against JAX-FEM, the only other "
"framework in the list above that supports end-to-end automatic "
"differentiation through the FEM pipeline."
msgstr ""
"反问题基准测试在一个经典的拓扑优化任务上检验 TensorMesh 的\\ **可微性**\\ "
"：使用带惩罚的各向同性固体材料法（SIMP）对二维悬臂梁进行柔度最小化。我们将其与 JAX-FEM "
"对比，后者是上述列表中唯一支持贯穿整个有限元方法流程的端到端自动微分的框架。"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:246
#: e89491437b9b4c0aa83d48cb6d3c6725
msgid "Problem setup"
msgstr "问题设置"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:248
#: df5f659068894905ab01cf1e9458f25b
msgid ""
"The computational domain is a rectangle :math:`\\Omega = [0, L_x] \\times "
"[0, L_y]` with :math:`L_x = 60` and :math:`L_y = 30` (dimensionless), "
"discretized into :math:`60 \\times 30` bilinear quadrilateral (QUAD4) "
"elements — 1,891 nodes and 1,800 elements. Homogeneous Dirichlet conditions "
"are imposed on the left edge,"
msgstr ""
"计算区域为矩形 :math:`\\Omega = [0, L_x] \\times [0, L_y]`\\ ，其中 :math:`L_x = 60`\\"
" 、\\ :math:`L_y = 30`\\ （无量纲），离散为 :math:`60 \\times 30` 个双线性四边形（QUAD4）单元 —— "
"共 1,891 个节点和 1,800 个单元。在左边界施加齐次狄利克雷条件，"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:254
#: 1f729db04a154bd98ea1928ecdc3e321
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{0} \\quad \\text{on } \\Gamma_D = \\{(x,y) : x = 0\\},"
msgstr "\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{0} \\quad \\text{on } \\Gamma_D = \\{(x,y) : x = 0\\},"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:258
#: 9edc332aa59747ceab2810e07f44b86c
msgid ""
"and a distributed traction is applied to the lower portion of the right "
"boundary,"
msgstr "并在右边界的下部施加分布牵引力，"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:261
#: e31808c403794e2d87a26864358034cf
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\mathbf{t} = (0,\\, -100)^\\top \\;\\text{N/m}\n"
"\\quad \\text{on } \\Gamma_N = \\{(x,y) : x = L_x,\\; 0 \\leq y \\leq 0.1\\, L_y\\}."
msgstr ""
"\\mathbf{t} = (0,\\, -100)^\\top \\;\\text{N/m}\n"
"\\quad \\text{on } \\Gamma_N = \\{(x,y) : x = L_x,\\; 0 \\leq y \\leq 0.1\\, L_y\\}."

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:266
#: 70b344348f8e4276b344160b3863653b
msgid "Cantilever boundary conditions"
msgstr "悬臂梁边界条件"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:271
#: 897240d54b9146c3b87211eb17b36c6f
msgid "The element stiffness is parameterized by the SIMP interpolation"
msgstr "单元刚度由 SIMP 插值参数化"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:273
#: 226633d5991b414bbeebd3d8d2c98c5e
#, python-brace-format
msgid "E(\\rho) = E_{\\min} + \\rho^p \\,(E_{\\max} - E_{\\min}),"
msgstr "E(\\rho) = E_{\\min} + \\rho^p \\,(E_{\\max} - E_{\\min}),"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:277
#: a66fa5ec305743bfad131e8234875357
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\rho \\in [\\rho_{\\min}, 1]` is the element-wise density (the"
" design variable), :math:`p = 3` penalizes intermediate densities, "
":math:`E_{\\max} = 70{,}000` MPa is the solid stiffness, and "
":math:`E_{\\min} = 70` MPa keeps the stiffness matrix non-singular. The "
"Poisson's ratio is :math:`\\nu = 0.3`."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`\\rho \\in [\\rho_{\\min}, 1]` 是逐单元密度（设计变量），\\ :math:`p = 3` "
"对中间密度进行惩罚，\\ :math:`E_{\\max} = 70{,}000` MPa 为实体刚度，\\ :math:`E_{\\min} = "
"70` MPa 用以保持刚度矩阵非奇异。泊松比为 :math:`\\nu = 0.3`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:283
#: 708f6627b4904c5983eeb8a360583ad2
msgid ""
"The optimization minimizes structural compliance subject to a volume "
"constraint:"
msgstr "该优化在体积约束下最小化结构柔度："

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:286
#: 2bd40c7381a64c2e81fd4cb2c88badde
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"    \\min_{\\boldsymbol{\\rho}} \\quad\n"
"        & C(\\boldsymbol{\\rho})\n"
"          = \\mathbf{u}^\\top \\mathbf{K}(\\boldsymbol{\\rho}) \\mathbf{u}\n"
"          = \\mathbf{F}^\\top \\mathbf{u} \\\\\n"
"    \\text{s.t.} \\quad\n"
"        & \\frac{1}{|\\Omega|} \\int_{\\Omega} \\rho \\, d\\Omega \\leq \\bar{v} \\\\\n"
"        & \\mathbf{K}(\\boldsymbol{\\rho}) \\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{F} \\\\\n"
"        & \\rho_{\\min} \\leq \\rho_e \\leq 1, \\quad \\forall e\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"    \\min_{\\boldsymbol{\\rho}} \\quad\n"
"        & C(\\boldsymbol{\\rho})\n"
"          = \\mathbf{u}^\\top \\mathbf{K}(\\boldsymbol{\\rho}) \\mathbf{u}\n"
"          = \\mathbf{F}^\\top \\mathbf{u} \\\\\n"
"    \\text{s.t.} \\quad\n"
"        & \\frac{1}{|\\Omega|} \\int_{\\Omega} \\rho \\, d\\Omega \\leq \\bar{v} \\\\\n"
"        & \\mathbf{K}(\\boldsymbol{\\rho}) \\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{F} \\\\\n"
"        & \\rho_{\\min} \\leq \\rho_e \\leq 1, \\quad \\forall e\n"
"\\end{aligned}"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:299
#: 4969388c404f4d8bba5198dc81ad312b
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"with target volume fraction :math:`\\bar{v} = 0.5` and :math:`\\rho_{\\min} "
"= 10^{-3}`. We use the Method of Moving Asymptotes (MMA) with move limit "
":math:`\\Delta\\rho_{\\max} = 0.1` and a sensitivity filter of radius "
":math:`r_{\\min} = 1.5\\,h` (where :math:`h` is the element size) to "
"suppress checkerboard patterns. The optimization runs for 51 iterations."
msgstr ""
"目标体积分数为 :math:`\\bar{v} = 0.5`\\ ，\\ :math:`\\rho_{\\min} = 10^{-3}`\\ "
"。我们采用移动渐近线法（MMA），移动限制为 :math:`\\Delta\\rho_{\\max} = 0.1`\\ ，并使用半径为 "
":math:`r_{\\min} = 1.5\\,h`\\ （其中 :math:`h` 为单元尺寸）的灵敏度过滤器以抑制棋盘格图案。优化共运行 51 "
"次迭代。"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:307
#: 27399fed60354be595595fbf1ef604a2
msgid "Sensitivity via automatic differentiation"
msgstr "通过自动微分计算灵敏度"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:309
#: 5567ee3f12574c43b58fd6f94f74a176
msgid "The classical adjoint-method sensitivity for SIMP has the closed form"
msgstr "SIMP 的经典伴随法灵敏度具有如下闭式表达"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:311
#: 3734cadf9cb8409ba758edc5e27dd2e1
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\frac{\\partial C}{\\partial \\rho_e}\n"
"= -p\\, \\rho_e^{p-1} (E_{\\max} - E_{\\min})\\,\n"
"  \\mathbf{u}_e^\\top \\mathbf{K}_0^e \\mathbf{u}_e,"
msgstr ""
"\\frac{\\partial C}{\\partial \\rho_e}\n"
"= -p\\, \\rho_e^{p-1} (E_{\\max} - E_{\\min})\\,\n"
"  \\mathbf{u}_e^\\top \\mathbf{K}_0^e \\mathbf{u}_e,"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:317
#: 63ba935f04bc46f58667aba420e5812b
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\mathbf{K}_0^e` is the element stiffness at unit Young's "
"modulus. In TensorMesh this gradient is **not implemented manually** — it is"
" obtained by backpropagating through the differentiable assembly and sparse "
"solve via PyTorch's reverse-mode autograd. The closed-form expression above "
"is reproduced only for reference and as a consistency check against the "
"autograd output."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`\\mathbf{K}_0^e` 是单位杨氏模量下的单元刚度。在 TensorMesh 中，这一梯度\\ **并非手动实现** ——"
" 而是通过 PyTorch 的反向模式 autograd 对可微的装配和稀疏求解进行反向传播得到。上述闭式表达仅作参考，并用于与 autograd "
"输出进行一致性检查。"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:325
#: 5d31bc62fb3f4ada8f13a8d2814c8f5d
msgid "Final design comparison"
msgstr "最终设计对比"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:327
#: a7920980f171453a90c448294a4fbc9c
msgid ""
"Both frameworks converge to the same canonical truss-like topology, and "
"TensorMesh runs noticeably faster end-to-end thanks to GPU-resident assembly"
" and solve."
msgstr "两个框架都收敛到同样经典的桁架状拓扑，而得益于装配与求解全程驻留在 GPU 上，TensorMesh 的端到端运行速度明显更快。"

#: ../../source/performance/benchmarks.rst:331
#: b4b6fb5c29fd42e48ec72720b16ce2fb
msgid "Final compliance and topology comparison"
msgstr "最终柔度与拓扑对比"

